## .github/

```text
.github/
├── FUNDING.yml
├── GOOD_FIRST_ISSUES.md       # 15 条可领取入门任务
├── RELEASE_GUIDE.md           # 维护者首次发布指南
├── PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md
├── ISSUE_TEMPLATE/
│   ├── bug_report.yml / case_request.yml / showcase.yml / config.yml
└── workflows/
    ├── ci.yml                       # PR + push 都跑：lint + build + worker typecheck
    ├── deploy-docs.yml              # main 改动 docs/ 或 worker/ 时：build + R2 增量 + worker deploy + smoke
    └── scheduled-cases-test.yml     # 每天 02:00 UTC+8 跑全部案例校验，失败开 issue
```

